 | 2026-04-14 | presentation_surfaces_ui_pipeline_20260405 | Cover and loading surface background resolution uses a simplified convention: outputs/{scene_program_name}/base.png. Actual scene rendering may place the output elsewhere. | Medium | Open | Align with the scene assembler output convention; prefer passing an explicit resolved image path rather than deriving it from the manifest name. |
